# Frontend Core Standards

## Syntax & Style
- **TypeScript Strictness**: NO `any` types. Use strict interfaces.
- **Functional Components**: Use `const Component = () => {}` syntax.
- **Styling**:
  - Use **Tailwind CSS** exclusively.
  - Use `clsx` or `cn` (shadcn utility) for conditional classes.
  - NO CSS Modules or styled-components.
- **Imports**: Always use absolute imports with the `@/` alias (e.g., `@/components/ui/button`).

## Directory Structure (App Router)
- **`app/`**: Routes and Pages only.
- **`components/`**: All React components.
- **`lib/`**: Utilities and helper functions.
- **`actions/`**: Server Actions for data mutation.